{"tid":1650611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話核彈都唔割？","createTime":"2019-10-13T05:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T06:31:09.000Z","uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09da7a4e4e530670080fa409fcbe7e27f501fe46","tid":1650611,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"因為雨傘完全失敗的經驗，雨傘做過乜今日再做就係等於失敗就會屌就恨<br />\n<br />\n當日大家都冇做錯,無人贏無人輸一個城市嘅變革唔係一朝一夕改變到的事，香港人對抗緊係世上唯一最大極權中國共產黨，一個反人類集體意志，名義上世上唯一實權共產國家，佢哋會不惜一切維護僅存的意志，權力的統治<br />\n<br />\n只有團結微小嘅力量先可以有能力對抗國家級武力，是一個殺人的國度，自8964開始已經沒有掩飾所做的惡行，過去死的是中國人對你們說可能沒有關係但死的未來的是香港人<br />\n<br />\n你們還會垂死掙扎的話 團結 唔好口講核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n香港人 絕不妥協"},{"pid":"c9fdfea71d42d7ea79f55ae92f37f18788e4b98e","tid":1650611,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"😡留番啲怒氣<br />\n生存<br />\n反抗"},{"pid":"831654606b664a378d07e10f8da452e334bcad84","tid":1650611,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4ecc1657d7f87ff1f091af9a3de68acc97b5ba","tid":1650611,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebdfc903620c361c002c42367613ad664470cdd","tid":1650611,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7909a3c1ac2865286e52acef7803a7a3853e6c","tid":1650611,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e265c1c0d30d4a97c7a92c112152d5886665922c","tid":1650611,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" cl